dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jerry Green. May I have your name, please?
Hello, Jerry. My name is Martha Walker.
Great, nice to meet you, Martha. I will need a couple of details to assist you further. Can you provide me with your policy number, please?
Sure, my policy number is three two six eight nine.
Thank you, Martha. One more thing, could you confirm the make and model of your vehicle for verification purposes?
Yes, it's a two zero one five Honda Civic.
Thank you for providing that information, Martha. I will now check our records to assist you with your inquiry. Please hold on for a moment.
I have verified your details, Martha. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
No, that's all I needed. Thank you for your help, Jerry.
You're welcome, Martha. If you have any more questions in the future, don't hesitate to reach out. Have a great day.
